## What happened

I saw this exception from the device selector when opening an exiting Flutter project. I have noticed this exception generally after upgrading my IntelliJ version (perhaps w/ the upgrade to 2021.1?).

## Version information

IntelliJ IDEA `2021.1.2` • Flutter plugin `io.flutter 57.0.6-dev.5` • Dart plugin `211.7233`

Flutter 2.3.0-17.0.pre.299

## Exception

Trying to reset custom component in a presentation
